t-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #3db249;\">support@lookout.com</a>.<br><br>\n\nTo learn more about how Lookout can protect your enterprise against threats such as Pegasus, visit <a class=\"green\" href=\"https://click.email.lookout.com/?qs=66467b9e77c7070039940743bac09363a0166205309a2a987a6e16989a64abbefeee2a8dd437c99a\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #3db249;\">our enterprise blog post</a>.<br><br>\n\n\n<strong>Your Account Information:</strong><br>\nEmail address: jeeproject@yahoo.com<br>\nDevice type: iPhone41<br>\nPhone number ending in: no phone number on record\n\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n\n\n          </font>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n            \n          \n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n              <td height=\"20\">\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            \n            <tr>\n  <td>\n    <table class=\"footer\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; text-align: center; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n  <td>\n    <table cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"learn-more\" border=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; width: 100%; max-width: 650px; font-size: 16px; text-align: left; border-top: 1px solid #e1e1e1; border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e1e1; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"middle\">\n          <span class=\"link\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: auto; text-align: left; color: #3db249; padding: 0; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n    <a href=\"https://click.email.lookout.com/?qs=66467b9e77c70700d323f8f2a6a145b7c48416f